precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument (REVOCATION OF SURRENDER) assented to by the
LONG PLAIN FIRST NATION BAND OF INDIANS which revokes the 1951 surrender of
the petroleum, natural gas and mineral leasing rights affecting the whole
of Long Plain Indian Reserve No. 6 in Manitoba.
